crypto: marvell - Don't hardcode block size in mv_cesa_ahash_cache_req

Don't use 64 'as is', as max block size in mv_cesa_ahash_cache_req. Use
CESA_MAX_HASH_BLOCK_SIZE instead, this is better for readability.

